when you're at band practice.

00:31:20.375 --> 00:31:22.583
[chuckles] Sorry, pretty.

00:31:22.666 --> 00:31:23.375
[scoffs]

00:31:23.458 --> 00:31:26.333
What about the three-in-one wedding?

00:31:27.208 --> 00:31:28.375
[clicks tongue]

00:31:28.458 --> 00:31:30.166
Dad still wants to do it.

00:31:30.750 --> 00:31:32.541
Babe, help me out.

00:31:32.625 --> 00:31:34.583
Maybe you know someone for Fadly.

00:31:34.666 --> 00:31:35.791
[hums] Sure.

00:31:35.875 --> 00:31:38.583
By the way, I'm going to Jakarta tomorrow

00:31:38.666 --> 00:31:40.166
to prepare for the engagement.

00:31:40.250 --> 00:31:41.958
Whew, we're going to Jakarta?

