Don't go begging.

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:11.333
It's a disgrace to our family.

00:33:12.750 --> 00:33:16.000
[phone buzzing]

00:33:18.041 --> 00:33:20.000
Fadly! Where are you going?

00:33:20.916 --> 00:33:23.166
I wasn't done talking.

00:33:23.250 --> 00:33:24.708
[Fadly] What now?

00:33:25.208 --> 00:33:27.083
[Nisa] Take me away, Fadly.

