00:33:37.250 --> 00:33:38.375
[Nisa sobs]

00:33:39.291 --> 00:33:40.666
I want to elope.

00:33:41.208 --> 00:33:43.583
-Oh my God. Eloping?
-[Mustafa] Hey!

00:33:44.250 --> 00:33:45.291
No!

00:33:45.875 --> 00:33:49.750
