00:33:54.250 --> 00:33:55.291
Yes, Dad.

00:33:56.625 --> 00:33:58.083
[Pirre] Cheer up, Fadly.

00:33:58.166 --> 00:33:59.666
Life's like a wheel.

00:33:59.750 --> 00:34:03.708
Sometimes you're down,
but sometimes you're at rock bottom.

00:34:03.791 --> 00:34:05.916
-[cackles]
-[Ariping] Shut up.

00:34:06.625 --> 00:34:09.916
What do you need, boss?
How can we help you?

