00:34:49.166 --> 00:34:50.583
What should I do?

00:34:50.666 --> 00:34:52.333
Shush!

00:34:55.375 --> 00:34:56.458
[music stops]

00:35:00.708 --> 00:35:02.583
-Dewi?
-Yes.

00:35:02.666 --> 00:35:03.500
I'm Fadly.

00:35:06.750 --> 00:35:07.916
Have a seat.

00:35:11.583 --> 00:35:13.583
[witty music]

00:35:15.875 --> 00:35:17.916
