00:35:20.208 --> 00:35:21.583
How are you, Dewi?

00:35:21.666 --> 00:35:22.708
I'm okay.

00:35:25.166 --> 00:35:26.416
How's your dad?

00:35:27.500 --> 00:35:28.666
He passed away.

00:35:28.750 --> 00:35:31.208
Inna Lillahi wa inna ilaihi raji'un.

00:35:32.416 --> 00:35:33.625
I mean…

00:35:34.208 --> 00:35:35.208
How's your mother?

