I'm an orphan.
I live alone with my little brother.

00:35:40.125 --> 00:35:41.500
Oh.

00:35:42.083 --> 00:35:43.083
I see.

00:35:43.166 --> 00:35:44.416
[Fadly] I'm sorry.

00:35:45.416 --> 00:35:46.583
How is he doing?

00:35:46.666 --> 00:35:50.541
He's staying in the hospital right now.

00:35:50.625 --> 00:35:52.250
Want to visit him?

00:35:53.375 --> 00:35:56.250
Anyone? Help.

00:35:56.333 --> 00:36:02.375
["Celengan Rindu"
by Fiersa Besari playing]

00:36:14.458 --> 00:36:16.125
-[woman] Fadly!
-[music stops]

00:36:16.208 --> 00:36:17.041
Yes, ma'am?

00:36:17.125 --> 00:36:19.875
[scoffs] Ma'am?

00:36:19.958 --> 00:36:21.958
It's me, Niken.

00:36:22.041 --> 00:36:22.958
From Tunder.

00:36:28.958 --> 00:36:30.250
Oh, Niken.

00:36:30.333 --> 00:36:31.625
Sorry.

00:36:32.625 --> 00:36:33.875
