That's enough dating apps for me.

00:37:31.583 --> 00:37:33.958
[song ends]

00:37:34.041 --> 00:37:35.333
What's up, brother?

00:37:35.416 --> 00:37:37.500
Why the bad mood out of nowhere?

00:37:37.583 --> 00:37:38.708
Chill.

00:37:38.791 --> 00:37:40.750
Remember what happened
at the cafe yesterday?

00:37:40.833 --> 00:37:44.708
