[Mustafa] Ahmad, everything ready?

00:41:04.833 --> 00:41:07.625
Yes, Dad. Our flight is at five
in the evening tomorrow.

00:41:08.083 --> 00:41:08.916
Dear.

00:41:09.000 --> 00:41:09.708
