00:41:21.125 --> 00:41:23.916
It's ivory, dear.
The shade of elephant tusks.

00:41:24.000 --> 00:41:25.250
Okay.

00:41:25.333 --> 00:41:28.916
But I think I'll wear this one.

00:41:29.000 --> 00:41:31.375
This looks more elegant.
