00:41:31.458 --> 00:41:32.625
-[Ahmad] Yes, Mom.
-[Fatimah] Right?

00:41:32.708 --> 00:41:34.541
-Sure.
-[Fatimah] Good.

00:41:34.625 --> 00:41:36.791
I'll put it in the suitcase.

00:41:45.666 --> 00:41:46.791
[knocking]

00:41:47.833 --> 00:41:48.833
Fadly.

00:41:48.916 --> 00:41:52.041
I'm borrowing this to take to Jakarta.

00:41:53.750 --> 00:41:54.791
Take it.

