-Babe, where's your cousin?
-Hm?

00:44:04.541 --> 00:44:06.750
She's late, but she's almost here.

00:44:08.958 --> 00:44:10.833
She's late. Just wait.

00:44:13.583 --> 00:44:15.125
[woman] Peace be upon you.

00:44:15.208 --> 00:44:17.000
-And upon you peace.
-[Asha exclaims]

00:44:17.083 --> 00:44:19.291
[dramatic music]

00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:37.833
Top-tier spices, right?

00:44:39.875 --> 00:44:42.833
-This is Asha's cousin.
-Oh.

00:44:43.583 --> 00:44:45.083
Subhanallah.

00:44:45.166 --> 00:44:46.541
[Asha's mom]
You're getting more beautiful.

00:44:51.625 --> 00:44:52.958
[Asha's dad] When are you getting married?

