She's doing taaruf?
Why didn't you tell me?

00:45:08.166 --> 00:45:10.291
I just found out too, babe.

00:45:15.125 --> 00:45:16.333
Sorry, brother.

00:45:18.833 --> 00:45:20.416
-[Asha] Hi.
-Asha.

00:45:20.500 --> 00:45:21.333
Congratulations.

00:45:21.416 --> 00:45:23.041
