-Sorry I'm late.

00:45:23.125 --> 00:45:25.958
It's okay. This is my fiancé, Ahmad.

00:45:26.041 --> 00:45:27.250
-Peace be upon you.
-Hello.

00:45:27.333 --> 00:45:30.500
