-Fadly.

00:45:33.958 --> 00:45:37.416
The guy that wanted to see me?

00:45:37.500 --> 00:45:38.625
[clears throat]

00:45:38.708 --> 00:45:40.375
[chuckles]

00:45:40.458 --> 00:45:45.416
["Celengan Rindu"
