00:46:25.666 --> 00:46:27.500
Hey, Rifa.

00:46:27.583 --> 00:46:28.291
[chuckles]

00:46:29.625 --> 00:46:31.250
Don't look at him, he's going crazy.

00:46:31.333 --> 00:46:32.958
Peace be upon you, Rifa.

00:46:33.583 --> 00:46:35.166
[whispers] No, no.

00:46:35.250 --> 00:46:36.541
[groans]

00:46:37.791 --> 00:46:39.541
Huh, Rifa?

00:46:40.083 --> 00:46:41.291
I haven't seen you around.

00:46:42.833 --> 00:46:46.166
